you're going to get

00:18:45.280 --> 00:18:48.500 align:middle line:84%
the most change is by
starting in the area where

00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:49.300 align:middle line:90%
you're the weakest.

00:18:49.300 --> 00:18:50.020 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Great awareness.

00:18:50.020 --> 00:18:50.380 align:middle line:90%
>>SHIMOFF: Yep.

00:18:50.380 --> 00:18:51.180 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:18:51.180 --> 00:18:53.980 align:middle line:84%
>>SHIMOFF: So the foundation
is taking responsibility

00:18:53.980 --> 00:18:54.950 align:middle line:90%
for your happiness.

