00:19:17.170 --> 00:19:18.468 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's a great point.

00:19:18.468 --> 00:19:20.260 align:middle line:84%
>>SHIMOFF: Really
important place to start.

00:19:20.260 --> 00:19:22.310 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, you're
